author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by GameMaker, the free, fast, and easy-to-use 2D game engine that’s helped power modern classics like UFO 50, Antonblast, and Yahtzee’s Starstruck Vagabond – https://opr.as/SecondWind-3 

After spending countless hours on the PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo, and Steam storefronts, Marty has come to the conclusion that they are all very terrible in their very own unique ways.
